 "title": "Masquerade Ball: A Night on Yavin (Part 5)",
 "summary": "In the closing hours of the masquerade aboard the Angry Rancor, the disguised Luke Skywalker finally lowers his Wookiee mask, having sensed a familiar presence at the party. The silver-tongued Rebel pilot draws the masked Lynae away for a private dance and a cryptic exchange of 'right answers.' At the bar, hostess Inanna trades easy conversation with Shael and the blue-winged Chyleni pilot Kyrin Sh'vani about an upcoming racing event, comparing notes on flying solo versus taking a co-pilot. Kyrin departs to corral a badly singing drunk, and the gathering settles into warm, unguarded camaraderie as the festivities draw to a close.",
